00:02:21,740 --> 00:02:24,378
{\an1}Who the hell are you!?

5
00:02:24,411 --> 00:02:27,884
{\an1}One who seeks to reform
the Land of Wind!

6
00:02:32,393 --> 00:02:34,831
{\an1}I won't let you escape!

7
00:02:42,678 --> 00:02:45,382
