10
00:02:55,602 --> 00:02:57,071
Punishment!

11
00:02:58,240 --> 00:02:59,910
<i>(Temari)</i>
<i>Take cover!</i>

12
00:03:02,413 --> 00:03:04,785
[explosion]

13
00:03:17,608 --> 00:03:19,012
