<i>You wanted to talk to me?</i>

17
00:03:31,601 --> 00:03:36,208
{\an1}Please, Gaara...
forget about supervising
the Chunin Exams.

18
00:03:36,242 --> 00:03:39,381
{\an1}The people targeting you are
stepping up their efforts.

19
00:03:39,415 --> 00:03:43,590
{\an1}You'll just be
playing into their hands
if you continue this.

