because of that...

22
00:03:48,130 --> 00:03:51,303
{\an1}...it would be like declaring
that I will cave under pressure.

23
00:03:51,337 --> 00:03:54,241
Yeah, maybe so,
but still...!

24
00:03:54,275 --> 00:03:56,814
<i>...It's just the </i>
<i>Chunin Exams!</i>

25
00:04:01,455 --> 00:04:07,131
<i>(Gaara)</i>
<i>The Chunin Exams is where</i>
<i>everything began for me.</i>

26
00:04:08,166 --> 00:04:12,109
{\an1}Thanks to him, I've
made it to this day.

27
00:04:13,142 --> 00:04:19,220
{\an1}So I'm going to make sure
these Chunin Exams are a
success.

28
00:04:27,569 --> 00:04:30,408
<i>(Shibire)</i>
<i>We've finally reached</i>
<i>Hidden Sand territory.</i>

29
00:04:30,441 --> 00:04:32,310
{\an1}<i>And now on to the</i>
<i>second round's site!</i>

