is a long story...

49
00:05:45,211 --> 00:05:48,951
{\an1}Please, just let us rest
already. Plus, I'm starving!

50
00:05:48,984 --> 00:05:52,224
Seems so...

51
00:05:54,228 --> 00:05:57,200
We have never been to
the Hidden Sand before&

52
