{\an1}Although, to be accurate,
this isn't the Hidden
Sand Village.

54
00:06:03,611 --> 00:06:06,516
{\an1}In fact, we're actually
quite far away from it.

55
00:06:06,549 --> 00:06:09,755
{\an1}Are you saying you have
been to the Hidden Sand
Village before?

56
00:06:09,789 --> 00:06:12,360
Once on an errand
for the Hyuga.

57
00:06:12,393 --> 00:06:15,132
