00:06:19,807 --> 00:06:24,316
You know, taking the
Exams in a different
village is a bit stressful.

60
00:06:24,350 --> 00:06:28,724
{\an1}I wonder what the Second
Round is going to be like.

61
00:06:28,757 --> 00:06:31,963
{\an1}It'll probably be just like
the last Chunin Exams.

62
00:06:31,997 --> 00:06:35,068
{\an1}So we compete against
the other teams?

63
00:06:35,102 --> 00:06:37,339
