chance of that.

64
00:06:37,373 --> 00:06:41,246
{\an1}Then we are going to have
to be cautious of some teams.

65
00:06:41,281 --> 00:06:45,888
{\an1}We went at full-speed, and
yet we were not the first
to arrive here.

66
00:06:45,922 --> 00:06:49,061
{\an1}Yeah, the Hidden
Waterfall was the first.

67
00:06:49,094 --> 00:06:53,268
And not only that, but
they also arrived here
long before we did.

68
00:06:53,302 --> 00:06:57,509
{\an1}So just what kind of
opponents are they...?

69
