{\an1}I'm sorry, Fuu.

71
00:07:06,392 --> 00:07:08,495
{\an1}You'll just have to stay
in there until tomorrow
morning.

72
00:07:08,529 --> 00:07:11,301
<i>(Fuu)</i>
<i>What?! How come?!</i>

73
00:07:11,335 --> 00:07:14,106
{\an1}'Cause we never know what
you're gonna do next!

74
00:07:14,139 --> 00:07:18,114
{\an1}Please, just give us a break
and let us rest up for the
next round, all right?

75
00:07:18,147 --> 00:07:22,355
<i>(Fuu)</i>
<i>What?! But that means I can't go</i>
<i>and have fun with the others!</i>

76
00:07:22,389 --> 00:07:25,227
{\an1}That's just the kind of
thing that worries us!

77
00:07:25,260 --> 00:07:26,896
