78
00:07:29,201 --> 00:07:34,143
{\an5}<i>(Loudspeaker)</i>
<i>Dinner is now ready. Entrants,</i>
<i>please assemble in the</i>
<i>cafeteria.</i>

79
00:07:38,083 --> 00:07:39,954
