<i>So that's the Hidden Sand...</i>

80
00:07:39,987 --> 00:07:42,591
<i>(Kiba)</i>
<i>Yeah, just look at</i>
<i>them over there...</i>

81
00:07:42,624 --> 00:07:44,528
{\an1}... <i>giving everyone </i>
<i>the stink eye!</i>

82
00:07:44,561 --> 00:07:47,134
Those guys sure
do look mean...

83
00:07:47,167 --> 00:07:50,639
Yeah, but&You look
pretty mean, too, Kiba!

84
00:07:50,672 --> 00:07:53,812
{\an1}And over there is
the Hidden Rain...

85
00:07:53,845 --> 00:07:56,384
{\an1}<i>...I guess the other side</i>
<i>is the Hidden Grass.</i>

86
00:07:56,418 --> 00:07:59,088
<i>(Choji)</i>
<i>That guy is amazing...!</i>

87
00:07:59,122 --> 00:08:01,460
I would say so, too...!

88
00:08:01,493 --> 00:08:05,434
<i>Compared to him, even</i>
<i>our slightly chubby</i>
<i>Choji looks normal!</i>

89
00:08:05,467 --> 00:08:09,607
<i>(ino)</i>
<i>But the way he's sweating& </i>
<i>Seriously, that's gross.</i>

90
00:08:11,077 --> 00:08:14,983
<i>(Tenten)</i>
<i>Hey... I'm getting a </i>
<i>bad feeling here.</i>

91
00:08:15,018 --> 00:08:17,389
Hm? Bad feeling?

92
00:08:17,422 --> 00:08:22,198
{\an7}It's just all that sweat! If
he gets too close to the
food on the tables...

93
00:08:22,231 --> 00:08:24,535
{\an1}[horrified gasps]

94
00:08:26,905 --> 00:08:32,216
{\an1}All right! It looks like it's
just about time to eat dinner!

95
00:08:33,617 --> 00:08:34,954
[grunt]

96
00:08:34,987 --> 00:08:36,156
[nervous gasps]

97
00:08:37,325 --> 00:08:40,865
{\an1}Left foot... Right
foot... Left foot...

98
00:08:40,898 --> 00:08:42,568
{\an1}[squeamish groan]

99
00:08:46,308 --> 00:08:51,251
[grunts]

100
00:08:51,284 --> 00:08:53,522
{\an1}[grossed out groan]

101
00:08:53,555 --> 00:08:58,129
[sweat dripping]

102
00:08:58,163 --> 00:08:59,765
At this rate...

103
00:08:59,798 --> 00:09:02,337
{\an1}Our whole dinner's
gonna be...

104
00:09:06,612 --> 00:09:09,517
[shouts]

105
00:09:10,318 --> 00:09:13,758
Ahhhh!

106
00:09:14,860 --> 00:09:15,995
Whoa!

107
00:09:16,029 --> 00:09:18,366
<i>(Kiba)</i>
<i>Damnit!</i>

108
00:09:19,302 --> 00:09:20,803
[screaming]

109
00:09:20,837 --> 00:09:23,542
Eight Trigrams
Palm Rotation!

110
00:09:25,780 --> 00:09:27,783
{\an1}Thank goodness!
We're saved!

111
00:09:27,816 --> 00:09:29,920
Uh&No, I do not
think that we are!

112
00:09:29,954 --> 00:09:30,889
Huh?

113
00:09:37,969 --> 00:09:40,106
{\an1}What did you guys
do to our dinner?

114
00:09:40,139 --> 00:09:41,809
Yeah, what were
you thinking?

115
00:09:43,512 --> 00:09:46,818
{\an1}Why are you guys
disrespecting our friend?

116
00:09:46,851 --> 00:09:49,055
<i>(Rock Lee)</i>
<i>Please, do not misunderstand! </i>

117
00:09:49,089 --> 00:09:51,360
<i>(Rock Lee)</i>
<i>We only wanted to</i>
<i>protect our food!</i>

118
00:09:51,393 --> 00:09:56,269
{\an1}So you were just gonna save your
food and forget all about the
food for the rest of us?

119
00:09:56,302 --> 00:09:58,506
What're you
talking about?!

120
00:09:58,539 --> 00:10:00,477
We'd never
stoop to something
as low as that!

121
00:10:00,510 --> 00:10:04,016
{\an1}<i>Your suspicion just shows</i>
<i>that Gaara hasn't trained</i>
<i>you right!</i>

122
00:10:04,049 --> 00:10:08,558
{\an7}Did I hear you right?
Did you just criticize
Lord Gaara?

123
00:10:08,592 --> 00:10:11,930
{\an7}That is absolutely
unforgivable!

124
00:10:12,732 --> 00:10:14,902
{\an1}[fighting grunts]

125
00:10:16,406 --> 00:10:20,579
{\an1}Please stop this! Everyone,
please stop now!

126
00:10:25,756 --> 00:10:27,326
{\an1}[fighting grunts]

127
00:10:28,160 --> 00:10:30,831
{\an1}Ow!!!

128
00:10:30,864 --> 00:10:33,670
Hey, come on!
Knock it off!

129
00:10:39,046 --> 00:10:42,086
{\an1}Neji! Aren't you
going to stop them?!

130
00:10:42,119 --> 00:10:44,490
{\an1}Sorry, but I'm
busy right now.

131
00:10:44,523 --> 00:10:46,059
{\an1}Burami!

132
00:10:46,093 --> 00:10:50,735
{\an1}Hey, don't go eating
food off the floor!
Muyami! You help too!

133
00:10:50,769 --> 00:10:53,406
{\an1}I'll pass&I'm way
too shy to do that...

134
00:10:53,439 --> 00:10:55,276
{\an1}Calm down, every- -  Argh!

135
00:10:55,310 --> 00:10:57,113
{\an1}We must not fight- - ARGH!

136
00:10:57,781 --> 00:10:59,484
Why, you...!

137
00:10:59,517 --> 00:11:04,527
[groan]

138
00:11:05,461 --> 00:11:08,734
{\an1}Will you stop and
listen to me!?

139
00:11:17,048 --> 00:11:19,587
[gasp]

140
00:11:19,621 --> 00:11:24,128
{\an1}This room is too small for
a flashy move like that.

141
00:11:24,162 --> 00:11:28,871
{\an7}<i>I was not using my full</i>
<i>strength, but still, to</i>
<i>stop me with one hand&!</i>

142
00:11:28,905 --> 00:11:31,308
{\an1}What's that sound?

143
00:11:31,342 --> 00:11:34,414
{\an3}Fuu!

144
00:11:38,955 --> 00:11:40,592
Yaa!

145
00:11:41,294 --> 00:11:46,970
{\an1}Taa-daa! Well, well! Looks
like the party's already
started, huh, guys?!

146
00:11:47,003 --> 00:11:49,742
{\an1}<i>...Am I about to make</i>
<i>a hundred friends?</i>

147
00:11:49,776 --> 00:11:51,378
{\an1}Who are you?

148
00:11:51,412 --> 00:11:54,116
{\an1}I'm Fuu from the
Hidden Waterfall Village!

149
00:11:54,150 --> 00:11:56,254
{\an1}Uhh...

150
00:11:56,287 --> 00:11:58,625
<i>She's...</i>

151
00:11:58,658 --> 00:12:01,664
{\an1}I came to the Chunin Exams
to make a hundred friends!

152
00:12:01,698 --> 00:12:03,667
{\an1}and there's no better
time than right now!

153
00:12:03,702 --> 00:12:05,973
{\an1}So tell me, guys, what's
the plan for after dinner?

154
00:12:06,005 --> 00:12:10,915
{\an1}<i>Cards? Backgammon? Musical</i>
<i>chairs? You name it; I am</i>
<i>up for it!</i>

155
00:12:10,948 --> 00:12:14,320
{\an1}Or, how about all of us
