suffering, we have just
one life, this one.

179
00:13:38,808 --> 00:13:43,182
And to my mind, there
is only one truth to
be found in life.

180
00:13:43,215 --> 00:13:47,222
{\an1}There is only
one truth in life?

181
00:13:47,256 --> 00:13:51,765
Determination
never betrays you.

182
00:13:55,572 --> 00:13:59,813
Shira, you&

