185
00:14:10,733 --> 00:14:14,172
{\an1}As I reported, I wasn't able
to see Hanzo in person.

186
00:14:16,844 --> 00:14:20,417
{\an1}<i>...I tried to sneak back</i>
<i>in and investigate...but...</i>

187
00:14:33,040 --> 00:14:35,745
