191
00:14:48,101 --> 00:14:50,337
Well...

192
00:14:50,371 --> 00:14:57,484
{\an1}I expected just the
usual Chunin Exams.
But now that they're

193
00:14:57,518 --> 00:15:01,258
{\an1}underway, we're discovering
