200
00:15:22,898 --> 00:15:25,002
{\an1}Huh?

201
00:15:25,035 --> 00:15:27,639
{\an1}Oh! That's the
Sensei's quarters.

202
00:15:27,673 --> 00:15:28,641
The Sensei?!

203
00:15:29,344 --> 00:15:32,282
{\an1}Uh- Hey, Choji!

204
00:15:32,315 --> 00:15:35,989
<i>(Choji)</i>
<i>I'll bet they'll give us some</i>
<i>food if we go over there!</i>

205
00:15:36,022 --> 00:15:38,559
{\an1}But we're not supposed to
wander around at night!

206
00:15:38,592 --> 00:15:42,033
{\an1}e's so hungry that he's not even
